::Magmatron::

    He strapped Cheetor to the table for reprogramming. Lowering the 
programmer he stepped away from Cheetor and to the controls. Pressing the 
knobs and buttons he started to erase Cheetor's mind. Soon that was 
completed. He then started to reprogramm Cheetor into a model Destron 
warrior, loyal to Magmatron only, strong, powerful internal weapons, and a 
disposition to Predacons and Maximals alike.
    "Arise my new Warrior, and know that you belong to me," Magmatron said to 
Cheetor.
